amai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/71787a1ac9bfaf5273db8f59f621c690.webm?t=1749076992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/71787a1ac9bfaf5273db8f59f621c690.mp4?t=1749076992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use your nostalgic knowledge about the mixture of gunpowder<br></li><li> Collect items wisely so you don't run out of inventory space<br></li><li> Some items are hidden in the Dam, you need to find them to solve the level<br></li><li> The reloading tool is essential to crafting ammo, and the lockpick for unlocking<br></li><li> Some types of Gunpowder when combined repeatedly times create an enhanced type of ammunition<br></li><li> 40 challenging levels</li></ul>",
